{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"37f21b5f11","title":"李石生的右派反动言论","origin":"《云南省高等学校右派分子反动言论选集》(中国共产党云南省高等学校委员会办公室编印，1957.8.15)，内部资料 注意保存。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e4a3ac2a65","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":2,"articleId":"37f21b5f11"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"81d02828fd","name":"李燕生"},{"id":"98d4af9a09","name":"昆明医学院助教"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d77c707a88","type":"title","text":"李石生的右派反动言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"37f21b5f11"},{"id":"a93b028f37","type":"authors","text":"昆明医学院助教李石生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"37f21b5f11"},{"id":"38b7d7ac49","type":"paragraph","text":"[李石生：昆明医学院系统外科助教]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"37f21b5f11"},{"id":"5c82cc9418","type":"paragraph","text":"李石生从5月2日到6月14日作了几次发言，摘要如下：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"37f21b5f11"},{"id":"576845722d","type":"subtitle","text":"党对群众、知识分子有宗派","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"37f21b5f11"},{"id":"3e863d77df","type":"paragraph","text":"领导对下级公公平平是不可能的。对党员和非党员提的问题有不同的看法，对党员提的事就相信些，做得快些。很多人是爱我们国家，为什么会有这样情况呢？没有政治待遇，这当然是暂时的，不会永远存在。否则马列主义是骗人的。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"37f21b5f11"},{"id":"0ce667f1f7","type":"paragraph","text":"我有很多同学教书。他们反映当时不应教书，去学花脸还好些，因为他们钱拿的很多，而我吃粉笔灰的反而钱很少。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"37f21b5f11"},{"id":"f41ea42abb","type":"paragraph","text":"思想改造时搞老教师，使某些老教师不敢做事，闭口。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"37f21b5f11"},{"id":"5be6439605","type":"paragraph","text":"十二年赶上世界先进水平，主要靠这些书呆子。如果再把知识分子放在冰箱里，那怎么能搞好科学？","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"37f21b5f11"},{"id":"77eec640b6","type":"paragraph","text":"对进修问题为什么都要考虑家庭出身，试问，中国除了党团员，其他人是否都是饭桶？","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"37f21b5f11"},{"id":"148a3f1738","type":"appellation","text":"目前舆论界的批评也很差，使得正义不明，人与人之间，不公平的很多。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"37f21b5f11"},{"id":"bbaa321539","type":"paragraph","text":"我希望院方领导“亲贤臣，远小人”，别作印象统计。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"37f21b5f11"},{"id":"a6f036cd6e","type":"subtitle","text":"党只能在理论上高于一切","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"37f21b5f11"},{"id":"b31bcf5f23","type":"paragraph","text":"我反对把一切东西（技术）政治化。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"37f21b5f11"},{"id":"42bd257f17","type":"paragraph","text":"党高于一切，只是在理论上，处理内部事情就不能高一切。不能用马列主义就来解决问题阑尾，任何事不能只有一套公式。萝联先进经验是压人中国有很多专家，教学改革过去曾以“苏联先进经验”来压人，一个人应有民族自豪感。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"37f21b5f11"},{"id":"09f36cbf42","type":"paragraph","text":"过去虽有毛主席、但乌云满天","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"37f21b5f11"},{"id":"74c823b7f2","type":"paragraph","text":"过去虽有毛主席，但乌云满天。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"37f21b5f11"},{"id":"d5eb0db176","type":"paragraph","text":"如没有毛主席的报告，我是不敢讲话的。毛主席报告是救党内外的一切人，他教导党员不应该骑在人民头上。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"37f21b5f11"}],"page":{"id":"47d932d990","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"37f21b5f11","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}